		<h3>Log Mean Temperature Difference</h3>
		<img src="./help/minion64.png"/>
		</div>
		<p>
			This convenience model calculates the log mean temperature difference for a counter current heat exchanger.  The inputs are just the inlet and outlet temperatures, while the sole output is the <b>lmtd</b>.
		</p>
		<p>
			Note side 1 should be the hot side if you want a positive answer.
		</p>
